===Noun===
'''spade''' ([[spades]])

# A [[tool]] with a handle and a flat [[blade]] for [[dig]]ging.
# One of the [[suit]]s in a deck of cards, represented by a symbol shaped similarly to the blade of a spade (1).
# (offensive) A black person.

